<p><img src="/images/malta/beefbar/beefbar-24.jpg" alt="beefbar-24.jpg" /></p>

<p>Step outside to a seriously elegant and sophisticated terrace with huge loungers, canopied beach beds and a sparkling blue pool just begging you to dip you toe in. With pool bar service, butler service and that beautiful seascape, this is the place to be.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/beefbar/beefbar-12.jpg" alt="beefbar-12.jpg" /></p>

